Install the Dependencies
Run this command to install all the libraries used in your code:
code
Bash
npm install @google/genai lucide-react chart.js react-chartjs-2
Step D: API Key Configuration
Since you are running this locally, you need to set your API Key.
Create a file named .env in the root of your folder.
Add your key inside it:
code
Env
VITE_API_KEY=your_actual_google_api_key_here
Important: Vite uses import.meta.env.VITE_API_KEY by default. To make the existing code (which uses process.env.API_KEY)

npm run dev
